        <p> <strong>Our</strong> prices are not so expensive, they only start at Free and end by planting a Tree.
Transparency is our <em>key</em>, so per rental we take 1€ as an operating fee for planting trees. In return, you get to experience a really cool electric car for 2 hours for (Free) € and effectively help climate change by planting trees. After the first 2 hours our charge would be 18 cents per minute and feel free taking along trips as after 150 mins our pricing is automatically constant for 38€ every 24 hours.</p>
